{
  "stem": "17526.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I would never believe it, I never did believe it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And then towards the end, after about five, six days, the guards are lax.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "They-- they don't beat us, they opened the doors, we look out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And about on the eighth day or so, we-- I saw-- my first sight was a soldier shooting with a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] I know he's not a German, I didn't know he was American.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "It was an American.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "I didn't know he was an American.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And people are just running out of the wagons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I couldn't run, I could not walk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "I was laying among the dead on that train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "I couldn't make it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "So somebody helped me out from the wagon, and I was on the ground.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And I was laying there, where everybody that could walk was running towards the liberating soldiers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And there was a little town nearby, and what they did is they robbed, they pilfered.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "They slaughtered every chicken and every goat and every dog that they saw on the way and they robbed the Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "I was laying there until a Red Cross-- American Red Cross van came by.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "They picked me up on a stretcher, and they took me on this van.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And from there, the odyssey of hospitals started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember the name of the town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was on the ground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't near a town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was on the rails in the middle of nowhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there was a little town not far because later on, I was carried by there and I saw chaos, total chaos.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A-- a town with hundreds of refugees running around, robbing houses, throwing things out on the street.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
